      "topic": "WordPress-Developer-Checklist",
      "items": [
        {
          "title": "<p align=\"center\">\n<em>A user-friendly and fluid interface for using checklists.</em>\n</p><p align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<img alt=\"&gt;WordPress-Developer-Checklist\" src=\"dist/img/WordPress-Developer-Checklist-Animation.apng\" title=\"&gt;WordPress-Developer-Checklist\" width=\"800\"/>\n</a>\n</p><p><strong>Repository Status</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://opensource.org/licenses/Apache-2.0\"><img alt=\"License\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/License-Apache%202.0-red.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://GitHub.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/releases/\"><img alt=\"GitHub release\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/release/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://GitHub.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/commit/\"><img alt=\"GitHub commits\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/commits-since/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/1.0.0.svg\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/commits/master\"><img alt=\"Last deployed\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/last-commit/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/master.svg?label=last%20deployed&amp;style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist\"><img alt=\"Build Status\" src=\"https://travis-ci.org/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist.svg?branch=master&amp;style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/issues\"><img alt=\"GitHub issues\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/issues/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a></p><p><a href=\"https://GitHub.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/network/\"><img alt=\"GitHub forks\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/forks/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist.svg?style=flat-square&amp;label=Fork&amp;maxAge=2592000\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/stargazers\"><img alt=\"GitHub stars\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/stars/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://GitHub.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/watchers/\"><img alt=\"GitHub watchers\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/watchers/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist.svg?style=flat-square&amp;label=Watch&amp;maxAge=2592000\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Thomas-A-Reinert?tab=followers\"><img alt=\"GitHub followers\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/followers/Thomas-A-Reinert.svg?style=flat-square&amp;label=Follow&amp;maxAge=2592000\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://GitHub.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist/graphs/contributors/\"><img alt=\"GitHub contributors\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/contributors/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist.svg\"/></a></p><p><strong>Checklist/s Completion Status</strong></p><p><a href=\"\"><img alt=\"Prerequisites, Installation &amp; Post-Install\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Prerequisites%2C%20Installation%20%26%20Post--Install-80%25-yellowgreen.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"\"><img alt=\"Development\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Development-0%25-%23f00.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"\"><img alt=\"Security\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Security-0%25-%23f00.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"\"><img alt=\"Performance\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Performance-0%25-%23f00.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"\"><img alt=\"Theme-Development\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Theme--Development-0%25-%23f00.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a>\n<a href=\"\"><img alt=\"Plugin-Development\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Plugin--Development-0%25-%23f00.svg?style=flat-square\"/></a></p><p><strong>All the power of checklists, without the overhead:</strong>\n - User-friendly and fluid interface\n - Fast build with <a href=\"https://github.com/developit/preact\">Preact</a> and <a href=\"https://github.com/twbs\">Bootstrap4</a>\n - Generate PDF report\n - Offline checklists storage with LocalStorage\n - Auto-save your progress\n - <strong>Instant no-config app bundling</strong></p><p><strong>Use the online version:</strong>\n<a href=\"https://wpchecklist.tarthemes.com\">wpchecklist.tarthemes.com/</a></p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "topic": "Installation",
      "items": [
        {
          "title": "<p><strong>Install manually</strong></p><p>```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/Thomas-A-Reinert/WordPress-Developer-Checklist.git\nyarn install</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "topic": "How to use ?",
      "items": [
        {
          "title": "<p><strong>Build with <a href=\"https://github.com/gulpjs/gulp\">Gulp</a></strong>\n<code>bash\ngulp build</code>\nBuilt files are available in <code>dist</code> folder.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "topic": "Customize",
      "items": [
        {
          "title": "<p><strong>Build and serve files with <a href=\"https://github.com/gulpjs/gulp\">Gulp</a></strong>\n<code>bash\ngulp build\ngulp webserver</code></p><p>The version is available at <a href=\"http://localhost:8080\">http://localhost:8080</a></p>"
