    {
      "topic": "Troubleshooting",
      "items": [
        {
          "title": "<p>The new checklist does not appear in select:\n - Empty the localStorage before add a new checklist.\n - Try the Chrome extension <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/clear-session/maejjihldgmkjlfmgpgoebepjchengka\">\"Clear Session\"</a> to clear the localStorage for the current window</p>"
        }
      ]
